WEBVTT

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:06.789
Hi, my name is Brandon, and I have had

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:08.950
an experience with the Lord that he

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:10.629
keeps telling me I need to tell

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:12.870
people about. I've never really

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.749
talked in front of a camera before

00:00:15.759 --> 00:00:18.630
like this, but he wanted me to

00:00:18.640 --> 00:00:22.950
document it and tell everybody

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.349
what happened and what kind of

00:00:25.359 --> 00:00:27.910
experience I had with him. This

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:32.190
experience lasted all night long, and

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.709
I'm just asking the Holy Spirit right

00:00:34.719 --> 00:00:37.510
now to help me communicate

00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:40.630
everything that I saw.

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:43.350
It's really important because

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:45.830
Jesus Christ is coming, and he told me

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:49.069
he's coming face to face.

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:53.430
This experience happened on July

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:55.790
6th,

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:59.189
2014, and I've held it all these

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:01.189
years. I wrote it down on paper and

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.029
released it to some people on Facebook

00:01:03.039 --> 00:01:06.630
and to some church friends and family.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:12.550
Some people received it and some

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:16.149
people didn't. I'm just a

00:01:16.159 --> 00:01:18.469
deliverer of the message that he gave

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:24.590
me. I'm not here to argue about

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:28.670
theology

00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:28.680
or

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:32.230
try to convince anybody of my

00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:34.630
experience. I'm going to tell you

00:01:34.640 --> 00:01:37.630
exactly what happened, exactly how it

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:41.190
happened, from the beginning to

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.149
the end.

00:01:43.159 --> 00:01:46.230
I don't know if you're a mid-tribulation,

00:01:46.230 --> 00:01:46.240
post-tribulation,

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:51.230
or pre-tribulation believer.

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:57.630
Like I said, I'm not here

00:01:57.640 --> 00:02:00.870
to argue or try to get you to say

00:02:00.880 --> 00:02:03.270
anything in the comments about

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:06.149
what I saw or what I experienced.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:10.070
I'm just telling you what I saw and

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:12.190
we'll go from there.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:16.630
It all started out while I was asleep;

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:19.990
I went to bed a normal night,

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.990
nothing different. I went to sleep

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.630
and in the middle of my sleep, all of

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:27.350
a sudden, I don't know if I was in

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:30.470
my body or out of my body. I don't

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.509
know how it happened; all I

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:35.990
know is all of a sudden I was standing

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.589
with Jesus, and he was on my right

00:02:39.599 --> 00:02:42.869
hand the whole time in this experience.

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:46.589
He grabbed a hold of my hand and

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:51.910
I'll go from there. The first

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:55.750
scene, per se, of what I saw

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:57.750
was Jesus standing on my right

00:02:57.760 --> 00:03:00.390
hand. He had a hold of my hand and we

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.350
were in a town. I don't know what town

00:03:03.360 --> 00:03:05.910
we were in, but I know that there was a big

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:08.710
white building over to the

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:12.309
side. I was looking up

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:14.710
at this big white building and

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:17.350
at the sky, and the

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:20.470
sky was alive. It was like it was

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.670
moving; it was full

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:26.949
of lightning and very spooky

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:31.589
looking. I looked out over the

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:33.910
horizon and there was this

00:03:33.920 --> 00:03:37.430
lady running towards me, and she started

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.670
screaming. They were all screaming

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.670
in terror; they were all freaking out.

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:44.869
It was incredible.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:48.710
They were saying, "They're gone.

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.750
They're gone."I said, "Who's

00:03:51.750 --> 00:03:51.760
gone?"I

00:03:51.760 --> 00:03:53.430
told this lady,

00:03:53.440 --> 00:03:56.789
"Who's gone?"and she said, "Did you

00:03:56.799 --> 00:03:59.030
not see?"I said, "Did I not see

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.710
what, ma'am? What are you

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:02.869
talking about?"At this

00:04:02.879 --> 00:04:05.670
time, she could see me. Now, not every

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:07.509
time

00:04:07.509 --> 00:04:07.519
in

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:10.550
this experience were

00:04:10.560 --> 00:04:13.350
people able to see me.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:16.390
In this instance, she could

00:04:16.400 --> 00:04:19.509
not see Jesus, but she could see me.

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:22.390
She said, "The aliens? The

00:04:22.400 --> 00:04:25.070
aliens came and got the

00:04:25.070 --> 00:04:25.080
Christians."I

00:04:25.080 --> 00:04:28.469
said, "The

00:04:28.469 --> 00:04:28.479
aliens?"She

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:30.230
said, "Yes, they all

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:33.070
disappeared. They went

00:04:33.070 --> 00:04:33.080
up."At

00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:37.270
that moment, she just ran off.

00:04:37.280 --> 00:04:39.110
She was frantic, screaming in terror. She

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:41.590
ran as

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:43.469
fast as she could,

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:46.710
panicking. I looked out over the

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:49.189
horizon of the city. I was up on a

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:51.629
hill at this time and I could see

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:55.030
everything on fire. Everything was on

00:04:55.030 --> 00:04:55.040
fire—the

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:57.909
cars, the houses, the

00:04:57.919 --> 00:05:02.550
buildings. It was like

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.710
chaos beyond anything you could ever

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:07.590
comprehend was happening at this time.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:10.550
You could smell the smoke.

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:12.469
People were looting; they were stealing

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:14.150
out of cars

00:05:14.150 --> 00:05:14.160
and

00:05:14.160 --> 00:05:15.510
buildings. They were

00:05:15.520 --> 00:05:18.310
trashing the city

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:22.390
where I was. Jesus didn't

00:05:22.400 --> 00:05:26.070
say anything. In fact, he never

00:05:26.070 --> 00:05:26.080
spoke;

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:28.790
I could perceive his thoughts when he

00:05:28.800 --> 00:05:31.430
was touching my hand. I knew what he was

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:33.909
thinking, but he never said anything out

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:36.790
of his mouth. He could understand what I

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:39.350
was thinking, but I never said anything

00:05:39.350 --> 00:05:39.360
to

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.909
him.

00:05:41.919 --> 00:05:44.390
I was just looking across the city,

00:05:44.390 --> 00:05:44.400
thinking,

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:47.430
"Oh my gosh, what is going

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:47.440
on?"All

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:51.909
of a sudden, we translated. We

00:05:51.919 --> 00:05:55.430
left that spot and went to

00:05:55.440 --> 00:05:58.310
another spot. He grabbed my

00:05:58.310 --> 00:05:58.320
hand—we

00:05:58.320 --> 00:05:59.990
were still holding hands—but it was like

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.550
we just

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.830
disappeared and came to another

00:06:04.840 --> 00:06:08.670
time. In this time frame,

00:06:08.670 --> 00:06:08.680
I

00:06:08.680 --> 00:06:10.670
was

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:13.990
looking over Europe. I knew I was

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.510
looking over Europe because I was

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:17.590
standing back, like I was watching a

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:19.990
movie. It was very strange. I

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:23.029
was looking out over Europe and

00:06:23.039 --> 00:06:24.510
I saw this

00:06:24.520 --> 00:06:29.270
man in Berlin. All the

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:32.309
world leaders were behind a table. It

00:06:32.319 --> 00:06:34.870
was a round table in Berlin. It

00:06:34.880 --> 00:06:38.390
looked like a big office.

00:06:38.390 --> 00:06:38.400
It was a

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:40.390
brown table, and there

00:06:40.390 --> 00:06:40.400
were

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:42.950
chairs all around it. All of these

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:45.830
world leaders were

00:06:45.840 --> 00:06:49.749
behind this big table,

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:51.909
and this man—I didn't know who he

00:06:51.919 --> 00:06:54.870
was at the time,

00:06:54.870 --> 00:06:54.880
but

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:57.749
I'll tell you later—and all of the

00:06:57.759 --> 00:07:01.990
people were asking him for help.

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:04.150
They were asking him for a solution to

00:07:04.160 --> 00:07:06.390
all the rioting and the craziness

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:10.870
that was going on. He was

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:14.230
instructing them on what to do. He had

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:18.150
all the wisdom and was very

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:20.790
powerful in demeanor, the way he carried

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:24.790
himself. He was wearing a gray suit,

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:27.510
and he was a Middle Eastern

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:32.629
man. All of a sudden, that

00:07:32.639 --> 00:07:37.270
scene was over, but the

00:07:37.280 --> 00:07:39.909
Lord at that time spoke to me about a

00:07:39.919 --> 00:07:42.550
scripture and showed me

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:44.950
how everyone would give over their

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:48.150
kingdoms to him within one hour.

00:07:48.150 --> 00:07:48.160
As

00:07:48.160 --> 00:07:50.189
I said, I'm not a Bible

00:07:50.199 --> 00:07:53.670
scholar or a theology major;

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:56.790
I'm just a guy who loves Jesus

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:59.270
and seeks Him with all my

00:07:59.280 --> 00:08:01.350
heart, and I had this experience with

00:08:01.360 --> 00:08:04.430
Him.

00:08:04.440 --> 00:08:09.350
The next scene I see is

00:08:09.350 --> 00:08:09.360
this man

00:08:09.360 --> 00:08:13.430
on TV—he's on

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:17.430
CNN, Fox, and

00:08:17.430 --> 00:08:17.440
everywhere.

00:08:17.440 --> 00:08:20.550
He is telling all the people

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:24.230
of the world what happened to the

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:26.710
people who disappeared,

00:08:26.720 --> 00:08:31.589
explaining

00:08:31.599 --> 00:08:34.070
that they were rebellious,

00:08:34.070 --> 00:08:34.080
that

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:36.750
they were taken away out of

00:08:36.760 --> 00:08:39.110
rebellion, and that they were being

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:41.029
punished. All these people were

00:08:41.029 --> 00:08:41.039
punished—it

00:08:41.039 --> 00:08:43.190
was the Christians, and they

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.790
were all being

00:08:44.800 --> 00:08:47.430
taken out. Then he

00:08:47.430 --> 00:08:47.440
explained

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:49.269
that he was the new leader of

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:53.990
the world. I looked out and

00:08:56.590 --> 00:08:56.600
saw

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:02.150
how he was gradually taking power. I want to

00:09:02.150 --> 00:09:02.160
tell

00:09:02.160 --> 00:09:05.269
you

00:09:05.279 --> 00:09:07.430
what I

00:09:07.440 --> 00:09:10.070
felt;

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:12.350
this is very

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:14.949
important: everybody wakes up every

00:09:14.959 --> 00:09:17.630
single day with a

00:09:17.630 --> 00:09:17.640
peace

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:20.990
they don't realize they

00:09:21.000 --> 00:09:24.389
have. They go to bed with it

00:09:24.389 --> 00:09:24.399
and

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.389
wake up with it. Even the worst

00:09:26.399 --> 00:09:30.870
sinner in the world has a form of

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:32.630
peace inside of them that they don't

00:09:32.640 --> 00:09:33.550
even

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:37.230
realize. When the rapture

00:09:37.240 --> 00:09:40.350
happens and we're taken

00:09:40.360 --> 00:09:45.590
out, there is a void of peace like

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:49.910
I've never felt in all of my life;

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:52.829
it blankets the

00:09:52.839 --> 00:09:55.590
earth. I used to think that the Holy

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:59.110
Spirit left with us because He dwells in

00:09:59.120 --> 00:10:00.949
each Christian. He dwells in us, and

00:10:00.959 --> 00:10:03.590
when we invite him into our heart,

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.990
I believe that he went with us when

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:08.630
the rapture happened. I

00:10:08.630 --> 00:10:08.640
cannot

00:10:08.640 --> 00:10:10.990
back that up biblically. I don't

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:15.269
know. All I know is that there is no

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:19.150
prayer covering, there is no sense of

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:22.550
peace, there is no joy. It is

00:10:22.560 --> 00:10:24.269
absolute

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:27.310
chaos. And this

00:10:27.320 --> 00:10:31.590
man has a sense that whenever everybody

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:34.389
looks at him, when everybody is

00:10:34.399 --> 00:10:36.509
gazing upon

00:10:36.519 --> 00:10:40.310
him, a false sense of peace is what I

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:43.590
want to say. He

00:10:43.600 --> 00:10:46.710
brings a peace when he is on the TV. He

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:50.949
brings a sense of comfort that

00:10:50.959 --> 00:10:53.430
everybody wants to follow him so quickly

00:10:53.440 --> 00:10:54.870
because they are so scared and everybody

00:10:54.870 --> 00:10:54.880
is

00:10:54.880 --> 00:10:57.829
so tormented. They all turn

00:10:57.839 --> 00:11:01.269
to him so quickly out of that peace that

00:11:01.279 --> 00:11:03.990
he brings, but it is dirty.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:06.590
I don't know how to describe

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:10.550
it. So he is on the TV, and he

00:11:10.550 --> 00:11:10.560
is

00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:13.829
telling everybody what happened to

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:17.870
the Christians. Then I see

00:11:17.880 --> 00:11:20.030
people in

00:11:20.030 --> 00:11:20.040
the

00:11:20.040 --> 00:11:23.670
Iran and Iraq area over

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:23.680
there—Pakistan,

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:26.269
that area over there—they were

00:11:26.279 --> 00:11:29.829
rejoicing. And they were all calling out

00:11:29.839 --> 00:11:33.910
and saying the Mahdi has come. The

00:11:33.910 --> 00:11:33.920
Mahdi

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.310
has come. And I don't know what

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:39.430
that means. I have studied it

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:42.710
now a little bit more. I

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:44.230
don't know what I'm allowed

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:47.030
to say about all this as

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:49.590
far as on YouTube and what will be

00:11:49.600 --> 00:11:51.670
allowed. I don't want my video to get

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:54.870
flagged, but they were calling it the

00:11:54.870 --> 00:11:54.880
Mahdi.

00:11:54.880 --> 00:11:56.670
They were calling him the

00:11:56.670 --> 00:11:56.680
Mahdi.

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.350
And so everybody was calling

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:03.269
him the Mahdi. And so he

00:12:03.269 --> 00:12:03.279
was himself

00:12:03.279 --> 00:12:06.629
Middle Eastern. He was a Muslim. I

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:10.230
know this because he said he was and he

00:12:10.240 --> 00:12:14.470
had a... Okay, I won't get

00:12:14.480 --> 00:12:17.269
to that part yet. Okay, this is what

00:12:17.279 --> 00:12:22.790
happens next. I see him come on TV,

00:12:22.800 --> 00:12:25.590
and he is telling everybody to bring

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:28.550
their Bibles into the stadiums, into

00:12:28.560 --> 00:12:30.870
these areas. He said, 'If you see a

00:12:30.880 --> 00:12:33.590
Bible, it is mandated by law that

00:12:33.600 --> 00:12:36.470
everybody brings these Bibles into these

00:12:36.470 --> 00:12:36.480
areas.'And

00:12:36.480 --> 00:12:40.350
so, it was like

00:12:40.350 --> 00:12:40.360
courthouses,

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:42.949
places like that. They were

00:12:42.959 --> 00:12:45.550
all like police stations, things like

00:12:45.560 --> 00:12:49.190
that. He brings these Bibles in and they

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:52.870
start stacking them

00:12:52.870 --> 00:12:52.880
up—big

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.710
shelves full. There were thousands,

00:12:54.720 --> 00:12:57.350
millions of Bibles just everywhere. And

00:12:57.360 --> 00:12:59.829
everybody just willfully

00:12:59.839 --> 00:13:01.509
did it; they just brought

00:13:01.519 --> 00:13:03.350
in the Bibles. And I remember seeing

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.629
them everywhere. There were stacks and

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:07.590
stacks of Bibles everywhere. And so they

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:10.550
would write down your name on a piece of

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:12.710
paper of who brought the Bible and what

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:14.710
it was or whatever. And he told

00:13:14.720 --> 00:13:17.430
everybody, 'If you want to come and

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:19.190
check out the Bible and look at it, it

00:13:19.190 --> 00:13:19.200
is okay.'We'll

00:13:19.200 --> 00:13:22.150
let you. It was kind

00:13:22.150 --> 00:13:22.160
of

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.389
a trick, though, because whenever

00:13:24.399 --> 00:13:28.069
people came in and wrote on

00:13:28.079 --> 00:13:30.069
the paper to check out their Bible that they brought in—if they wanted to look at

00:13:30.069 --> 00:13:30.079
it

00:13:30.079 --> 00:13:31.750
again—you

00:13:31.760 --> 00:13:34.710
were

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:38.550
marked even more so. And so it was

00:13:38.560 --> 00:13:41.509
like you

00:13:41.509 --> 00:13:41.519
were

00:13:41.519 --> 00:13:43.190
being watched. It was a surveillance

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:46.710
state. It was really weird. It

00:13:46.710 --> 00:13:46.720
was

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:48.710
like a library, is

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:51.190
what I want to call it. Within a couple

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:56.430
of months, I would say I saw

00:13:56.440 --> 00:14:01.430
a football field with piles of Bibles,

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:03.750
probably three or four stories

00:14:03.760 --> 00:14:06.150
high. It was massive—just massive.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:09.189
They were all being burned. All the

00:14:09.199 --> 00:14:12.870
Bibles were burned by his order.

00:14:12.880 --> 00:14:15.350
Like I said,

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:16.949
the gasoline was all over

00:14:16.959 --> 00:14:18.230
them. They were thrown into the fire, and

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:20.150
it was incredible. Just

00:14:20.160 --> 00:14:22.310
massive amounts of smoke and the Bibles

00:14:22.320 --> 00:14:24.910
all burning.

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:32.230
Then I saw these flags

00:14:32.240 --> 00:14:34.629
that he put on every single courthouse.

00:14:34.639 --> 00:14:36.949
If you had a country flag, like the

00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:38.710
United States of America or Europe,

00:14:38.720 --> 00:14:41.350
those flags were taken down

00:14:41.360 --> 00:14:44.870
and his flag was put up. It

00:14:44.880 --> 00:14:48.790
was black,

00:14:51.760 --> 00:14:56.590
green, and white, and it had these

00:14:56.600 --> 00:15:00.470
gold swords that were all in the

00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:03.710
center of

00:15:03.710 --> 00:15:03.720
it—massive

00:15:03.720 --> 00:15:07.189
swords, like a

00:15:11.519 --> 00:15:13.509
saber, is what I want to call it. It

00:15:13.509 --> 00:15:13.519
was

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:15.350
a massive sword in

00:15:15.360 --> 00:15:19.269
the center of this thing, and each color

00:15:19.279 --> 00:15:21.030
represented

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:25.590
a terrorist group, ISIS

00:15:28.920 --> 00:15:32.150
and others. I'm not going to even

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:34.389
go there because I don't know

00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:36.389
all their names, but

00:15:39.839 --> 00:15:42.710
each was

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:44.870
a terrorist group,

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:47.590
and they're all being thanked for

00:15:47.600 --> 00:15:52.150
bringing in his reign

00:15:52.160 --> 00:15:55.030
because they supported this so much.

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:03.749
After that,

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:11.749
he puts his flag on the

00:16:11.759 --> 00:16:15.670
buildings, and then this is

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:18.389
what happens next. I go with

00:16:18.399 --> 00:16:21.189
Jesus to this other area. In this, I

00:16:21.199 --> 00:16:26.790
see people on Fridays. Every Friday,

00:16:26.800 --> 00:16:29.749
you're required to worship him. Every

00:16:29.759 --> 00:16:33.110
Friday, they all had white outfits on.

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:36.230
Every person in the world was required

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:39.670
to wear a white outfit, and they had

00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:42.389
white garments on their heads. The women

00:16:42.399 --> 00:16:45.110
did. And men had white garments on their

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:47.829
heads. They had white robes on and

00:16:47.839 --> 00:16:51.670
they were all in single file lines.

00:16:51.680 --> 00:16:55.430
Every line was

00:16:55.440 --> 00:16:58.470
perfect and they were all side by side.

00:16:58.480 --> 00:17:00.230
You were required to get on

00:17:00.240 --> 00:17:03.630
your knees and worship.

00:17:03.640 --> 00:17:08.470
I saw these massive screens—huge screens

00:17:08.480 --> 00:17:12.150
all on the side of the

00:17:12.160 --> 00:17:14.549
buildings of these courthouses. On

00:17:14.559 --> 00:17:16.949
Fridays, he would appear wherever you

00:17:16.959 --> 00:17:20.510
were. If it was America or Europe or

00:17:20.520 --> 00:17:23.270
whatever, you would go to this place of

00:17:23.280 --> 00:17:25.510
worship on Fridays and look at

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:27.590
the screen. They would

00:17:27.600 --> 00:17:31.190
worship him at those screens and it was

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:32.470
all over the place, but they were always

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:33.830
in white robes. They were always in

00:17:33.830 --> 00:17:33.840
these

00:17:33.840 --> 00:17:36.390
single lines and it was in

00:17:36.400 --> 00:17:39.510
town square areas. What's

00:17:39.520 --> 00:17:43.029
really interesting is that I

00:17:43.039 --> 00:17:45.590
watch a lot of videos on YouTube of

00:17:45.600 --> 00:17:47.830
people walking tours and stuff.

00:17:47.840 --> 00:17:50.630
There's a place in Rome that I saw that

00:17:50.640 --> 00:17:53.830
it happens at. There are places

00:17:53.840 --> 00:17:57.430
in my town where I live now.

00:17:57.440 --> 00:17:59.270
There's a place here and there's a place in

00:17:59.280 --> 00:18:01.750
another town not too far from me

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:05.669
where

00:18:05.679 --> 00:18:09.029
it's being required to worship.

00:18:10.679 --> 00:18:14.549
Very interesting stuff. So Christians

00:18:14.549 --> 00:18:14.559
left.

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:19.750
Then it goes off of him and I

00:18:19.760 --> 00:18:25.270
see Christians that were left. Now,

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:27.270
this is the part that gets hard, and

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:29.230
there's probably a lot of

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:33.350
you that will disagree with this

00:18:33.350 --> 00:18:33.360
or

00:18:33.360 --> 00:18:36.630
get angry about it, but I have to

00:18:36.640 --> 00:18:39.270
tell you what I saw. It is

00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:42.350
what it is.

00:18:42.360 --> 00:18:46.590
A lot of the grace message that was

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:49.430
preached, people lived a compromising

00:18:49.440 --> 00:18:51.190
lifestyle.

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:54.430
They were living like the

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:59.430
world and they got left.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:01.430
There were literally thousands

00:19:01.440 --> 00:19:04.630
of Christians here that

00:19:04.640 --> 00:19:06.230
thought they were born again, thought

00:19:06.240 --> 00:19:07.669
that they were living right, and thought

00:19:07.679 --> 00:19:10.789
that they did everything right, but they

00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:13.510
didn't. They were living like the world

00:19:13.520 --> 00:19:16.470
and had an appearance of godliness.

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:18.230
Their hearts were so far from the Lord,

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:19.990
but they thought they were with him.

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:21.830
They were the ones that even like

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:24.070
the Bible talks about: 'You prophesied in my

00:19:24.080 --> 00:19:27.990
name, you cast out devils in

00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:29.830
my name, you healed the sick in my name.

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:31.590
Depart from me; I never knew

00:19:31.600 --> 00:19:33.070
you.'That's

00:19:33.080 --> 00:19:35.909
what happened. There

00:19:35.909 --> 00:19:35.919
were Christians

00:19:35.919 --> 00:19:37.669
everywhere. There

00:19:40.080 --> 00:19:43.830
were pastors that I saw

00:19:43.830 --> 00:19:43.840
who

00:19:43.840 --> 00:19:47.750
preached that

00:19:47.750 --> 00:19:47.760
watered-down

00:19:47.760 --> 00:19:51.190
grace message who were left here

00:19:51.200 --> 00:19:54.310
in punishment because

00:19:54.320 --> 00:19:56.830
they were preaching a lukewarm

00:19:56.840 --> 00:20:00.549
gospel. They were left here, and

00:20:00.559 --> 00:20:05.669
those people were as mad as could

00:20:05.669 --> 00:20:05.679
be.

00:20:05.679 --> 00:20:09.430
It was terrible. They

00:20:09.440 --> 00:20:13.190
were after those preachers that preached

00:20:13.200 --> 00:20:15.270
that way. They said, "You lied to

00:20:15.280 --> 00:20:18.549
us. You didn't tell us the

00:20:18.549 --> 00:20:18.559
truth."I

00:20:18.559 --> 00:20:20.150
was standing with Jesus the whole time.

00:20:20.160 --> 00:20:22.870
He said to me, "Look at this. Watch

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:26.150
this. Remember this."He didn't say

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:28.070
it, but I heard his thoughts. He said,

00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:32.149
"Watch this. Look at

00:20:32.149 --> 00:20:32.159
this."I

00:20:32.159 --> 00:20:35.750
was gazing upon this area.

00:20:35.760 --> 00:20:38.470
I knew after all this

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:41.270
happened I was back in time, back

00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:43.270
before the Antichrist was taking over.

00:20:43.280 --> 00:20:44.950
This is at the beginning,

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:47.909
right after the rapture happens.

00:20:47.919 --> 00:20:52.390
The people are mad. They are very

00:20:52.400 --> 00:20:56.149
angry that they're here. The

00:20:56.159 --> 00:20:58.710
pastors and these leaders—I saw some of

00:20:58.720 --> 00:21:00.310
them, and I'll never mention their names

00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:02.789
because the Lord told me not to. I saw

00:21:02.799 --> 00:21:05.350
people that were on TV

00:21:05.360 --> 00:21:07.750
teaching the gospel on TBN and stuff

00:21:07.760 --> 00:21:10.549
like that—those Christian channels that

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:14.310
were actually left. Some of them

00:21:14.310 --> 00:21:14.320
were—like

00:21:14.320 --> 00:21:16.470
two or three. I'm not ever going to

00:21:16.480 --> 00:21:18.630
say who they were, but I'm going to tell

00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:20.390
you that they were here. There were some

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:24.470
folks here, and they

00:21:24.470 --> 00:21:24.480
were

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:28.549
very angry

00:21:28.559 --> 00:21:31.510
and ready to kill

00:21:31.510 --> 00:21:31.520
them.

00:21:31.520 --> 00:21:34.909
It was awful. I

00:21:34.919 --> 00:21:37.070
saw one angry

00:21:37.070 --> 00:21:37.080
Christian

00:21:37.080 --> 00:21:41.669
lady that I know very well.

00:21:41.679 --> 00:21:44.230
I worked at a church for 13

00:21:44.240 --> 00:21:46.870
years; I was a janitor there. She

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:48.310
was one of the members there at the

00:21:48.320 --> 00:21:51.350
church where I was. I was looking up,

00:21:51.360 --> 00:21:54.310
and she looked up at the heavens and

00:21:54.320 --> 00:21:56.710
she flipped the Lord off. She gave the

00:21:56.720 --> 00:21:59.870
Lord the middle finger and she said some expletives,

00:21:59.870 --> 00:21:59.880
and

00:21:59.880 --> 00:22:04.350
it was very

00:22:04.360 --> 00:22:07.190
bad. I was watching them all just

00:22:07.200 --> 00:22:09.990
turn on God. They were angry,

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:12.549
turning on people. There

00:22:12.549 --> 00:22:12.559
were

00:22:12.559 --> 00:22:15.549
groups of them that were building

00:22:15.559 --> 00:22:18.870
colonies. They started saying, "We've got to

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:20.950
get prepared. It's fixing to get really

00:22:20.960 --> 00:22:23.830
bad. We've got to get our stuff around.

00:22:23.840 --> 00:22:26.110
We know what's happened. We know what's

00:22:26.110 --> 00:22:26.120
coming."A

00:22:26.120 --> 00:22:29.430
lot of them did. "We've got

00:22:29.440 --> 00:22:31.430
to go to the mountains. We've got to go

00:22:31.440 --> 00:22:33.990
to places of refuge. We've got to go now

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.590
because we're running out of time. This

00:22:35.600 --> 00:22:37.470
is fixing to get bad really

00:22:37.470 --> 00:22:37.480
fast."I

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:42.149
saw these people

00:22:42.159 --> 00:22:45.029
try to have a camaraderie. There

00:22:45.029 --> 00:22:45.039
were

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:48.070
families that were left. And this is

00:22:48.080 --> 00:22:50.029
another thing:

00:22:50.039 --> 00:22:56.390
everybody below the age of 15 was gone.

00:22:56.400 --> 00:22:59.430
All the little children were gone. All

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:02.630
of the younger teenagers

00:23:02.630 --> 00:23:02.640
and

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:05.430
pre-teens were gone. They all

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:08.310
got sucked up in the rapture. But

00:23:08.320 --> 00:23:10.950
anybody that was age of accountability and

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:13.669
older was left if you didn't know Jesus

00:23:13.679 --> 00:23:15.909
Christ and have a relationship with him.

00:23:15.919 --> 00:23:19.669
I watched these younger people

00:23:19.679 --> 00:23:20.990
go with their

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:24.310
families. During the

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:27.830
tribulation, I saw

00:23:27.830 --> 00:23:27.840
children

00:23:27.840 --> 00:23:30.390
being born. This part is

00:23:30.400 --> 00:23:34.590
really hard.

00:23:34.600 --> 00:23:39.029
I watched how

00:23:39.039 --> 00:23:41.909
the Christians all got together.

00:23:44.480 --> 00:23:47.190
They all go to

00:23:47.200 --> 00:23:49.390
these mountain

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:53.590
areas and dig massive holes in the side of

00:23:53.600 --> 00:23:58.230
the mountains. They

00:23:58.230 --> 00:23:58.240
were

00:23:58.240 --> 00:24:00.950
trying to keep warm because

00:24:00.960 --> 00:24:02.789
you couldn't stay in your

00:24:02.799 --> 00:24:05.669
house. You couldn't go into

00:24:05.679 --> 00:24:07.909
town and buy groceries because the

00:24:07.919 --> 00:24:09.590
mark of the beast is coming. I'm

00:24:09.590 --> 00:24:09.600
going

00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:12.950
to tell you about it; I saw how

00:24:12.960 --> 00:24:15.590
it happens, how the mark of the

00:24:15.600 --> 00:24:18.630
beast changes you, and how they put it

00:24:18.640 --> 00:24:20.870
in your forehead.

00:24:20.880 --> 00:24:23.669
I'll get to that—I don't want

00:24:23.679 --> 00:24:26.070
to skip around too much

00:24:26.070 --> 00:24:26.080
or

00:24:26.080 --> 00:24:28.710
make this too long

00:24:28.710 --> 00:24:28.720
as

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:30.549
I respect people's time.

00:24:34.760 --> 00:24:37.669
The Christians try to move

00:24:37.679 --> 00:24:41.909
at night. I was staying with

00:24:41.919 --> 00:24:44.710
Jesus, and he took me to

00:24:44.710 --> 00:24:44.720
a

00:24:44.720 --> 00:24:47.669
field. All I knew

00:24:47.669 --> 00:24:47.679
was it was

00:24:47.679 --> 00:24:50.149
dark outside, and the

00:24:50.159 --> 00:24:51.909
Christians were moving from place to

00:24:51.919 --> 00:24:53.510
place at night because they couldn't move

00:24:53.510 --> 00:24:53.520
during

00:24:53.520 --> 00:24:55.909
the day without being spotted. They

00:24:55.909 --> 00:24:55.919
were

00:24:55.919 --> 00:24:58.190
trying to get to places of

00:24:58.200 --> 00:25:00.830
safety.

00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:03.990
The farmers

00:25:04.000 --> 00:25:07.909
had guns like.22s and

00:25:07.919 --> 00:25:09.750
rifles, so there were still

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:11.510
firearms

00:25:11.510 --> 00:25:11.520
and

00:25:11.520 --> 00:25:14.710
ways of protection for farmers, but

00:25:14.720 --> 00:25:17.990
I didn't see many other people with guns.

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:20.710
The Christians didn't have guns. I

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:23.430
don't know

00:25:23.430 --> 00:25:23.440
why—nothing

00:25:23.440 --> 00:25:25.430
was really said about that—but I know

00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:27.350
the farmers did. I remember

00:25:27.360 --> 00:25:30.470
seeing one place where these

00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:32.870
Christians were trying to go through

00:25:32.870 --> 00:25:32.880
a

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:36.310
pasture, and dogs

00:25:36.320 --> 00:25:39.029
barking alerted the

00:25:39.039 --> 00:25:40.710
farmer inside the house. He flipped

00:25:40.720 --> 00:25:43.510
the light on, and he had a.22 in his

00:25:43.520 --> 00:25:45.909
hand. I know it was a.22. He fired

00:25:45.919 --> 00:25:49.190
it and called the authorities to

00:25:49.200 --> 00:25:51.990
tell them

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:55.990
people were moving at night. He didn't

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.350
know if they were Christians,

00:25:57.360 --> 00:25:58.470
but I knew they were.

00:26:01.640 --> 00:26:05.590
Then I saw men in black

00:26:05.590 --> 00:26:05.600
armored

00:26:05.600 --> 00:26:09.149
Hummer trucks

00:26:09.149 --> 00:26:09.159
with

00:26:09.159 --> 00:26:12.230
blue,

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:14.149
infrared-looking

00:26:14.159 --> 00:26:16.230
lights inside

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:18.230
the back.

00:26:18.240 --> 00:26:20.870
They were all black with

00:26:20.870 --> 00:26:20.880
blacked-out

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:23.190
windows. As

00:26:23.190 --> 00:26:23.200
they drove,

00:26:23.200 --> 00:26:25.269
the

00:26:25.279 --> 00:26:28.789
Christians tried to put cement

00:26:28.799 --> 00:26:31.430
blocks in the road to slow

00:26:31.440 --> 00:26:33.750
them down so they would have enough time

00:26:33.760 --> 00:26:36.149
to run away as fast as they could. They would try to throw things in the road to slow their approach, and they were running as

00:26:36.159 --> 00:26:38.149
fast as they could to try to get away.

00:26:49.360 --> 00:26:52.070
These men

00:26:52.080 --> 00:26:55.430
had black face masks on, like

00:26:55.440 --> 00:26:57.669
COVID masks,

00:26:57.669 --> 00:26:57.679
and

00:26:57.679 --> 00:26:59.909
black

00:26:59.919 --> 00:27:02.390
hoods, and they would jump out. They

00:27:02.400 --> 00:27:04.310
had black outfits on with these vests

00:27:04.310 --> 00:27:04.320
and

00:27:04.320 --> 00:27:06.630
would jump out of these

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:10.470
black cars with these guns. But

00:27:10.480 --> 00:27:12.149
this is what's weird: I've never seen

00:27:12.159 --> 00:27:13.990
one of these before. I've tried to

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:15.830
find them online and I can't;

00:27:15.840 --> 00:27:17.750
I've never seen this before. It was

00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:21.350
a pulse. They took these black guns and

00:27:21.360 --> 00:27:23.750
pointed them and

00:27:23.760 --> 00:27:25.830
shot, but it wasn't a

00:27:25.840 --> 00:27:28.230
bullet. It was electric,

00:27:28.240 --> 00:27:31.190
like an electromagnetic pulse,

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:33.350
and it just stuns you, but it didn't

00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:36.149
have any stun to it like the

00:27:36.159 --> 00:27:38.310
cords that come out like they have now.

00:27:38.320 --> 00:27:40.549
It was some kind of

00:27:40.559 --> 00:27:43.269
wave of energy that came

00:27:43.279 --> 00:27:45.110
out of these things and knocked you

00:27:45.120 --> 00:27:47.830
senseless for a couple of seconds. They

00:27:47.840 --> 00:27:50.789
didn't have to reload it; they just

00:27:50.799 --> 00:27:53.269
pointed it, and

00:27:53.279 --> 00:27:55.110
the people running fell out on the ground.

00:27:57.039 --> 00:27:59.590
They would pass out right there, and by

00:27:59.590 --> 00:27:59.600
the time

00:27:59.600 --> 00:28:01.269
they would get up, it was too

00:28:01.279 --> 00:28:04.070
late; they were held captive.

00:28:04.080 --> 00:28:07.789
These men would give them an

00:28:07.799 --> 00:28:11.630
ultimatum. I saw a

00:28:11.640 --> 00:28:15.750
woman and she had these two young

00:28:15.750 --> 00:28:15.760
children—a

00:28:15.760 --> 00:28:17.990
boy and a girl

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:19.830
born during the Tribulation. They

00:28:19.840 --> 00:28:22.310
were probably three or four

00:28:22.320 --> 00:28:24.590
years old, maybe more. They were

00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:29.190
talking, so they

00:28:29.190 --> 00:28:29.200
were young,

00:28:29.200 --> 00:28:32.470
maybe five.

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:34.909
They said, 'We're going to give the

00:28:34.919 --> 00:28:37.789
children the chip

00:28:37.799 --> 00:28:41.909
first, and if you don't deny your Jesus,

00:28:41.919 --> 00:28:44.149
we're going to cut your kids'heads off.

00:28:44.159 --> 00:28:46.950
We're going to cut their heads

00:28:46.950 --> 00:28:46.960
off.'Or

00:28:46.960 --> 00:28:49.430
you

00:28:49.440 --> 00:28:51.350
could take the chip. They gave

00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:55.870
them an ultimatum. The dad said,

00:28:55.880 --> 00:29:00.029
'No, we're not taking the mark. We will

00:29:03.110 --> 00:29:03.120
die.'The

00:29:06.240 --> 00:29:10.870
dad said, 'We're most

00:29:10.870 --> 00:29:10.880
certainly

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:12.789
not taking the mark.'The mother

00:29:12.799 --> 00:29:15.430
said, 'No, you can't cut my babies'heads

00:29:15.430 --> 00:29:15.440
off!'because

00:29:15.440 --> 00:29:17.830
the man had this huge

00:29:17.840 --> 00:29:20.630
sickle, a huge sword, in his hand. He was getting ready—he had

00:29:20.630 --> 00:29:20.640
the baby's head like this—and

00:29:20.640 --> 00:29:22.470
he was getting ready

00:29:25.600 --> 00:29:28.389
to just go and slice

00:29:28.399 --> 00:29:30.789
that kid's head off right there. There

00:29:30.799 --> 00:29:34.710
was no mercy. There was no conscience

00:29:34.720 --> 00:29:38.789
about it. It was just the way it was.

00:29:38.799 --> 00:29:41.269
And the dad cried out and said, "No, you

00:29:41.279 --> 00:29:46.389
must not take the mark."And when he

00:29:46.399 --> 00:29:50.230
said that, they cut his

00:29:50.240 --> 00:29:53.350
head off right there. And I'm talking it

00:29:53.360 --> 00:29:56.870
fell and rolled at my feet, and I could

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:59.909
smell his blood. That's how

00:29:59.919 --> 00:30:03.430
awful it was. Jesus stood there with me

00:30:03.440 --> 00:30:05.669
the whole time, and he never made a

00:30:05.679 --> 00:30:07.830
comment about it. He just told me to

00:30:07.840 --> 00:30:11.669
look. And so I looked and I watched

00:30:11.679 --> 00:30:14.470
the woman, and she said, "I'll take the

00:30:14.480 --> 00:30:16.710
mark. I'll take it. I'll take the

00:30:16.720 --> 00:30:19.590
chip. Don't take

00:30:19.600 --> 00:30:22.549
their heads."And this is what is so

00:30:22.559 --> 00:30:25.110
incredible; it's absolutely amazing

00:30:25.120 --> 00:30:29.389
about this part. They take this chip, and

00:30:29.399 --> 00:30:31.350
instantaneously those children were

00:30:31.360 --> 00:30:34.470
crying because they just saw their dad

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:37.269
die right in front of them. And the mom

00:30:37.279 --> 00:30:40.230
is crying and she's bawling her eyes out

00:30:40.240 --> 00:30:42.470
because she saw her husband die right in

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:45.269
front of her. And the moment she takes

00:30:45.279 --> 00:30:48.549
the chip, the baby, the two children, and

00:30:48.559 --> 00:30:50.269
her

00:30:50.279 --> 00:30:52.350
instantaneously lose

00:30:52.360 --> 00:30:55.190
emotion. They don't

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:57.029
have any emotion on their face.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:00.870
They totally lose the crying. It's

00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:02.870
like they went like a zombie right there

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:05.190
in front of me. Their minds and

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:07.750
everything had a peace again. It's like

00:31:07.760 --> 00:31:11.710
the chip sent a peace to their brain

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:16.070
somehow. I don't know how; all I

00:31:16.080 --> 00:31:18.630
know is the chip did something to them

00:31:18.640 --> 00:31:21.750
and it made them calm. It put off

00:31:21.760 --> 00:31:24.070
some kind of endorphin in them, and they

00:31:24.080 --> 00:31:27.510
just went cold in their face, like

00:31:27.520 --> 00:31:29.430
they're not there. It's like, "Hello,

00:31:29.440 --> 00:31:31.430
you're not there,"and they were not

00:31:31.440 --> 00:31:33.590
crying about him anymore. It's

00:31:33.600 --> 00:31:34.909
like they didn't

00:31:34.919 --> 00:31:40.870
care. And so I saw that, and then I

00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:45.029
saw a man trying to commit suicide, and

00:31:45.039 --> 00:31:47.750
he already had the mark. He had the chip

00:31:47.760 --> 00:31:50.310
in his hand, and he was standing on a

00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:53.990
major bridge, and all of a sudden the

00:31:54.000 --> 00:31:57.350
chip sent a signal to his brain and

00:31:57.360 --> 00:31:59.950
calmed him down and he did not kill

00:31:59.960 --> 00:32:02.870
himself. I don't understand why; I don't

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:05.830
understand how. All I know is that chip

00:32:05.840 --> 00:32:08.230
produced some kind of signal, some

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:11.269
kind of endorphin somehow, and calmed his

00:32:11.279 --> 00:32:13.230
mind down, and

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:15.750
instantaneously he became calm and he

00:32:15.760 --> 00:32:18.549
did not jump off that bridge. It

00:32:18.559 --> 00:32:21.029
knew; I don't know how it knew that you

00:32:21.039 --> 00:32:23.269
were fixing to do something like that.

00:32:23.279 --> 00:32:25.750
Then I would see people mowing their

00:32:25.760 --> 00:32:28.389
grass and I would walk by them, but they

00:32:28.399 --> 00:32:30.789
couldn't see me. I would walk by

00:32:30.799 --> 00:32:32.630
them and they were mowing, but they were

00:32:32.640 --> 00:32:35.269
not there. It's like you could go,

00:32:35.269 --> 00:32:35.279
"Hello,"but

00:32:35.279 --> 00:32:36.630
you were just in

00:32:36.640 --> 00:32:39.190
another world, way out there,

00:32:39.200 --> 00:32:41.750
like a zombie. It was weird.

00:32:41.760 --> 00:32:43.590
They were just mowing their grass

00:32:43.600 --> 00:32:46.149
like robots, but the chip would

00:32:46.159 --> 00:32:48.950
bring something to their

00:32:48.950 --> 00:32:48.960
biological

00:32:48.960 --> 00:32:52.430
brain. I don't get it.

00:32:52.440 --> 00:32:54.590
Another thing I thought was

00:32:54.600 --> 00:32:58.470
interesting is that I

00:32:58.480 --> 00:33:00.549
watched them. Jesus took me to a place

00:33:00.559 --> 00:33:02.909
in a town, and there were these

00:33:02.919 --> 00:33:06.389
barricades all over, massive

00:33:06.399 --> 00:33:09.669
gray barricades, huge.

00:33:09.679 --> 00:33:13.669
There were men with armed guards

00:33:13.679 --> 00:33:16.950
and guns all around.

00:33:16.960 --> 00:33:19.430
You would have to go

00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:21.830
through these barricades to get into

00:33:21.840 --> 00:33:25.029
these towns; you had to have your

00:33:25.039 --> 00:33:27.509
chip in your hand. If you

00:33:27.519 --> 00:33:29.990
didn't have the chip, you couldn't

00:33:30.000 --> 00:33:33.029
get in, and they would

00:33:33.039 --> 00:33:35.029
offer you the chip or you would die.

00:33:35.039 --> 00:33:36.789
They would kill you right

00:33:36.789 --> 00:33:36.799
there—no

00:33:36.799 --> 00:33:38.710
questions. If you didn't take

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:42.230
it, they'd cut your head off.

00:33:42.240 --> 00:33:45.190
There was a

00:33:45.190 --> 00:33:45.200
woman—I

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:48.070
remember her face. She was a white

00:33:48.080 --> 00:33:50.549
woman with brown hair, and she was

00:33:50.559 --> 00:33:53.110
standing in line.

00:33:53.120 --> 00:33:55.190
A lot of people, though not

00:33:55.190 --> 00:33:55.200
everyone,

00:33:55.200 --> 00:33:58.230
had a bruise on their

00:33:58.240 --> 00:34:01.350
head; it was a burn sore. The body

00:34:01.360 --> 00:34:04.990
had a reaction to the chip and it caused

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:08.149
sores on people's heads. It was like

00:34:08.159 --> 00:34:10.950
burn sores, and there were burn sores on

00:34:10.960 --> 00:34:13.510
their hands—not everyone, though.

00:34:13.520 --> 00:34:15.790
She was trying to mimic it with

00:34:15.800 --> 00:34:19.030
makeup, trying to put makeup on her

00:34:19.040 --> 00:34:22.710
hand to make it look like she had a burn

00:34:22.720 --> 00:34:24.030
sore.

00:34:24.040 --> 00:34:27.190
She was standing in line, and

00:34:27.200 --> 00:34:29.069
when she got up to go in through the

00:34:29.079 --> 00:34:32.310
gate, they saw that she was trying to

00:34:32.320 --> 00:34:35.109
fake it. People were so desperate

00:34:35.119 --> 00:34:37.990
for food and for whatever resources they

00:34:38.000 --> 00:34:40.550
could get into the towns

00:34:40.550 --> 00:34:40.560
that

00:34:40.560 --> 00:34:43.030
they were willing to do

00:34:43.040 --> 00:34:45.909
whatever it took. She was a Christian,

00:34:45.919 --> 00:34:48.149
basically. I guess I don't know who

00:34:48.159 --> 00:34:50.389
she really was;

00:34:50.399 --> 00:34:53.589
the moment they saw

00:34:53.599 --> 00:34:56.310
her faking it, they cut her head off

00:34:56.320 --> 00:35:00.109
right there. There was no time for even

00:35:00.119 --> 00:35:02.470
repentance. They just

00:35:02.480 --> 00:35:04.870
took a sickle-sword

00:35:04.870 --> 00:35:04.880
and

00:35:04.880 --> 00:35:06.870
cut her head off like it was

00:35:06.880 --> 00:35:08.870
nothing. Her head rolled out,

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:11.510
and people in line who were

00:35:11.520 --> 00:35:14.390
watching acted like it was nothing. There

00:35:14.400 --> 00:35:16.470
was no emotion. I'm telling you,

00:35:16.480 --> 00:35:18.550
there was no emotion to these people;

00:35:18.560 --> 00:35:21.750
they were gone. It was weird.

00:35:23.920 --> 00:35:25.510
I'm just telling you what I saw and I'm

00:35:25.520 --> 00:35:26.950
trying to figure it out myself. I'm still

00:35:26.950 --> 00:35:26.960
trying

00:35:26.960 --> 00:35:28.630
to figure out the nanotechnology. And the only thing

00:35:28.640 --> 00:35:31.349
that I think is really close to this nanotechnology

00:35:31.349 --> 00:35:31.359
is what

00:35:31.359 --> 00:35:34.950
a very

00:35:34.960 --> 00:35:37.829
rich man here in America is working

00:35:37.829 --> 00:35:37.839
on—I

00:35:37.839 --> 00:35:39.510
don't want to say his name. If you go

00:35:39.520 --> 00:35:42.150
and look at it, he's working on

00:35:42.160 --> 00:35:44.310
chips right now on pigs. That's all I

00:35:44.320 --> 00:35:47.510
can say. And it's very similar. But

00:35:47.520 --> 00:35:51.589
this chip goes—it's very small,

00:35:51.599 --> 00:35:54.069
like

00:35:54.069 --> 00:35:54.079
a

00:35:54.079 --> 00:35:58.550
very small square.

00:35:58.560 --> 00:36:01.430
I don't know how it gets power, if it

00:36:01.440 --> 00:36:03.430
gets it from your body's energy. I don't

00:36:03.440 --> 00:36:05.430
know, because it didn't have a battery.

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:07.510
There's no way a battery could be that

00:36:07.520 --> 00:36:11.030
small.

00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:12.870
Like I said, these men carried around

00:36:12.880 --> 00:36:14.790
these guns that were like waves of

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:16.870
energy and they knocked you down. It's

00:36:16.880 --> 00:36:20.550
like super sci-fi, but it's not.

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:23.349
It's legit what I saw.

00:36:24.839 --> 00:36:28.550
Then I

00:36:28.550 --> 00:36:28.560
saw

00:36:28.560 --> 00:36:32.069
the Christians again, and this

00:36:32.079 --> 00:36:33.430
is part of it.

00:36:33.440 --> 00:36:34.790
I'm praying I'm not skipping around too

00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:36.310
much, because I'm

00:36:36.320 --> 00:36:39.750
telling you how I remember it.

00:36:39.760 --> 00:36:41.470
They were digging these

00:36:41.480 --> 00:36:45.510
foxholes. And the winters were terrible.

00:36:45.520 --> 00:36:47.430
The further north they went in the

00:36:47.440 --> 00:36:50.310
mountains, the colder the temperatures

00:36:50.320 --> 00:36:52.390
were. I don't know what kind of

00:36:52.400 --> 00:36:55.030
catastrophic events of nature happened

00:36:55.030 --> 00:36:55.040
there,

00:36:55.040 --> 00:36:57.910
because I didn't see that. All I know

00:36:57.920 --> 00:37:02.069
is that the winters were awful, and

00:37:02.079 --> 00:37:05.950
people died from starvation and the

00:37:05.960 --> 00:37:09.910
cold quickly. It was bad.

00:37:09.920 --> 00:37:13.190
Here comes another part:

00:37:13.200 --> 00:37:16.030
I look up in the

00:37:16.040 --> 00:37:19.990
sky because I hear these noises,

00:37:20.000 --> 00:37:23.550
and there are thousands of drones.

00:37:23.560 --> 00:37:26.790
Thousands. No joke. Thousands. They

00:37:26.800 --> 00:37:30.069
are all in sequence with each other,

00:37:30.079 --> 00:37:33.190
flying across the sky,

00:37:33.200 --> 00:37:36.109
scanning the horizon and scanning

00:37:36.119 --> 00:37:39.910
everybody. The chip in

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:42.710
your hand or your forehead would report

00:37:42.720 --> 00:37:44.870
back to these

00:37:44.880 --> 00:37:48.390
drones that you had it. These

00:37:48.400 --> 00:37:50.150
drones would fly throughout the

00:37:50.160 --> 00:37:52.790
woods, throughout all areas, the

00:37:52.800 --> 00:37:54.710
oceans, everywhere. They were flying

00:37:54.720 --> 00:37:56.310
throughout all of America,

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:57.510
all over the place. You

00:37:57.510 --> 00:37:57.520
could

00:37:57.520 --> 00:37:59.430
literally

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:02.470
hear them coming, and they could sense

00:38:02.480 --> 00:38:05.349
your body heat,

00:38:05.359 --> 00:38:09.750
your motion, and everything. So, you

00:38:09.760 --> 00:38:12.390
couldn't hide from them. The only way I

00:38:12.400 --> 00:38:14.550
saw that the Christians could hide from

00:38:14.560 --> 00:38:17.630
them was digging into the side of the

00:38:17.640 --> 00:38:20.950
hills. The drones were looking for

00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:23.829
smoke or gunshots. So the Christians

00:38:23.839 --> 00:38:25.990
couldn't shoot for

00:38:25.990 --> 00:38:26.000
food—rabbits

00:38:26.000 --> 00:38:28.550
or deer or

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:31.190
anything that made noise—because the

00:38:31.200 --> 00:38:34.630
drones in the sky could hear

00:38:34.640 --> 00:38:37.670
the noises. They were alerted

00:38:37.670 --> 00:38:37.680
and

00:38:37.680 --> 00:38:40.710
would swarm to

00:38:40.720 --> 00:38:43.829
that area and see who did it. If you

00:38:43.839 --> 00:38:45.750
had the chip, it would report back and

00:38:45.750 --> 00:38:45.760
they would

00:38:45.760 --> 00:38:47.510
just go on

00:38:47.520 --> 00:38:50.069
about their business. But if you didn't

00:38:50.079 --> 00:38:52.150
have the chip, they would call for the

00:38:52.160 --> 00:38:53.910
authorities, who would come and

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:55.670
stay there until they

00:38:55.670 --> 00:38:55.680
arrived.

00:38:55.680 --> 00:38:57.990
You would run, but

00:38:58.000 --> 00:38:59.910
you couldn't get away. You couldn't get

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:01.190
away from them because they were up like

00:39:01.200 --> 00:39:04.230
a helicopter. They were flying over, and

00:39:04.240 --> 00:39:06.470
once they found you, you were done.

00:39:06.480 --> 00:39:08.790
They would come and either

00:39:08.800 --> 00:39:11.190
you took the chip or you took the

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:14.470
mark, or they cut your head off.

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:16.470
These

00:39:16.480 --> 00:39:18.550
Christians were all on the side of

00:39:18.550 --> 00:39:18.560
mountains—people

00:39:18.560 --> 00:39:21.030
that were still

00:39:21.040 --> 00:39:23.190
fighting to live and survive, who

00:39:23.190 --> 00:39:23.200
were

00:39:23.200 --> 00:39:26.069
not living for Jesus

00:39:26.079 --> 00:39:27.750
when they were on the

00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:30.910
earth, but they knew the truth. They

00:39:30.920 --> 00:39:33.069
knew.

00:39:33.079 --> 00:39:35.670
The children were the hardest part

00:39:35.680 --> 00:39:38.790
for me, those born during the

00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:40.790
Tribulation. I know there's a Bible

00:39:40.800 --> 00:39:42.390
verse that says, 'Woe to those that give

00:39:42.400 --> 00:39:45.829
suck in those days.'I believe that

00:39:45.839 --> 00:39:48.430
verse is talking about the

00:39:48.440 --> 00:39:51.150
Tribulation, but

00:39:51.160 --> 00:39:54.470
all I know is that the kids were

00:39:54.480 --> 00:39:56.870
taking it really hard.

00:39:56.880 --> 00:39:58.630
They were going inside, and the

00:39:58.640 --> 00:40:00.550
smoke was coming out of these

00:40:00.560 --> 00:40:02.230
caves. They were trying to keep the

00:40:02.240 --> 00:40:05.030
fires

00:40:05.040 --> 00:40:07.510
really low so that the drones

00:40:07.520 --> 00:40:10.550
couldn't see it. The drones

00:40:10.560 --> 00:40:12.710
would fly throughout the earth, and they

00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:16.230
sounded like swarms of bees beyond

00:40:16.240 --> 00:40:18.470
anything. It was

00:40:18.470 --> 00:40:18.480
incredibly

00:40:18.480 --> 00:40:20.310
loud. Swarms of bees were

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:21.510
everywhere, and you knew when they were

00:40:21.520 --> 00:40:23.030
coming because you could hear them from a

00:40:23.040 --> 00:40:25.510
distance. Everybody would scramble,

00:40:25.520 --> 00:40:28.069
trying to get into their safe zone as

00:40:28.079 --> 00:40:29.550
fast as they could to try to hide

00:40:29.550 --> 00:40:29.560
themselves.

00:40:29.560 --> 00:40:33.349
They

00:40:33.359 --> 00:40:36.790
were made to worship on Fridays. I

00:40:36.800 --> 00:40:40.910
told you about

00:40:40.920 --> 00:40:44.790
the people

00:40:44.790 --> 00:40:44.800
and

00:40:44.800 --> 00:40:46.390
the mark of the beast; they had the Abomination

00:40:46.390 --> 00:40:46.400
of Desolation

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:48.430
chip in their hands.

00:40:51.280 --> 00:40:54.470
Now I want to tell you about the

00:40:54.480 --> 00:40:58.349
Abomination of Desolation.

00:40:58.359 --> 00:41:01.870
I was all of a sudden translated to

00:41:01.880 --> 00:41:04.109
Israel, and

00:41:04.119 --> 00:41:08.630
I see this great big temple. It's on

00:41:08.630 --> 00:41:08.640
a

00:41:08.640 --> 00:41:12.230
hill, elevated,

00:41:12.240 --> 00:41:14.829
with

00:41:14.839 --> 00:41:19.510
these massive stone columns all

00:41:19.520 --> 00:41:23.270
inside of it and

00:41:23.270 --> 00:41:23.280
a

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:25.990
roof. There is

00:41:26.000 --> 00:41:28.470
a place

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:31.109
where

00:41:31.119 --> 00:41:34.470
people can come at the base of

00:41:34.480 --> 00:41:37.390
this temple.

00:41:37.400 --> 00:41:40.550
I'm standing

00:41:40.560 --> 00:41:43.109
at the base of

00:41:43.119 --> 00:41:45.910
the temple with Jesus,

00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:49.750
looking up.

00:41:49.750 --> 00:41:49.760
The

00:41:49.760 --> 00:41:51.750
temple

00:41:51.750 --> 00:41:51.760
is

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:55.270
elevated,

00:41:55.280 --> 00:41:57.670
and the Antichrist has a

00:41:57.680 --> 00:42:01.510
podium. He's standing in between

00:42:01.520 --> 00:42:06.309
those big columns with a man on either

00:42:06.309 --> 00:42:06.319
side of him.

00:42:06.319 --> 00:42:09.910
I don't know who

00:42:09.920 --> 00:42:12.230
this man is right here on his other

00:42:12.240 --> 00:42:14.790
hand. I believe he's another form of a

00:42:14.800 --> 00:42:17.030
religion. I'm not familiar with a lot of

00:42:17.040 --> 00:42:20.750
other leaders and other religious

00:42:20.760 --> 00:42:23.390
beliefs.

00:42:23.400 --> 00:42:29.630
I'll say that he had olive skin, lightning

00:42:29.630 --> 00:42:29.640
bolts,

00:42:29.640 --> 00:42:34.470
and darker hair also. But that's

00:42:34.480 --> 00:42:38.430
all I'm going to say about that.

00:42:38.440 --> 00:42:42.069
So, I'm looking up and there

00:42:42.069 --> 00:42:42.079
are

00:42:42.079 --> 00:42:46.150
lightning bolts shooting all over the

00:42:46.160 --> 00:42:50.790
sky. I'm talking—it's like

00:42:50.800 --> 00:42:54.630
total chaos, lightning—but none of

00:42:54.640 --> 00:42:56.470
it's touching the ground. It's just

00:42:56.480 --> 00:42:59.309
going all over the sky.

00:42:59.319 --> 00:43:03.589
And the Lord won't let me see his eyes

00:43:03.599 --> 00:43:07.390
from here, around all this.

00:43:07.400 --> 00:43:10.630
But I see the Antichrist again,

00:43:10.640 --> 00:43:13.510
and he's standing there proclaiming that

00:43:13.520 --> 00:43:16.710
he is God on the Temple Mount. And he

00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:19.910
has at this time—not every time

00:43:19.920 --> 00:43:22.230
that I see him, like when

00:43:22.230 --> 00:43:22.240
he was

00:43:22.240 --> 00:43:25.030
at the beginning

00:43:25.030 --> 00:43:25.040
when

00:43:25.040 --> 00:43:28.710
he first appears in Berlin—he didn't

00:43:28.720 --> 00:43:30.790
have a beard. I didn't see his eyes

00:43:30.800 --> 00:43:32.230
there, but I saw that he had

00:43:32.230 --> 00:43:32.240
olive

00:43:32.240 --> 00:43:34.230
skin and he was clean-cut

00:43:34.230 --> 00:43:34.240
and clean-shaven

00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:36.710
at this time. I don't

00:43:36.720 --> 00:43:40.150
know why. But at this time, he has a

00:43:40.160 --> 00:43:43.270
beard and it's salt and

00:43:43.270 --> 00:43:43.280
pepper—like

00:43:43.280 --> 00:43:45.109
black and

00:43:45.109 --> 00:43:45.119
white—a

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:48.870
beard, and the sides of his

00:43:48.880 --> 00:43:51.910
hair were black and white. They were not

00:43:51.920 --> 00:43:54.870
strictly white or strictly black. He had

00:43:54.880 --> 00:43:57.510
spots of gray coming through his

00:43:57.520 --> 00:44:00.630
hair similar to mine. But he had

00:44:00.640 --> 00:44:04.870
hair; he wasn't bald. He had a

00:44:04.880 --> 00:44:09.910
white turban hat on, like a

00:44:09.910 --> 00:44:09.920
rag-type

00:44:09.920 --> 00:44:12.750
garment on his head.

00:44:12.760 --> 00:44:16.390
I could see that—like I

00:44:16.400 --> 00:44:18.470
said, I couldn't see his eyes—but he had

00:44:18.480 --> 00:44:22.190
some kind of glasses on.

00:44:22.200 --> 00:44:25.710
He was about

00:44:25.710 --> 00:44:25.720
5'11"to

00:44:25.720 --> 00:44:31.430
6 feet tall from what

00:44:31.440 --> 00:44:32.950
I could see while looking up

00:44:32.960 --> 00:44:34.870
like this because it's in

00:44:34.880 --> 00:44:38.430
person now. He was probably

00:44:38.440 --> 00:44:44.950
around 195 to 215

00:44:44.950 --> 00:44:44.960
pounds

00:44:44.960 --> 00:44:47.829
in weight. I'll describe

00:44:47.839 --> 00:44:51.190
him like this: he carries himself like a

00:44:51.200 --> 00:44:54.390
James Bond. It may sound dumb, but

00:44:54.400 --> 00:44:56.150
I'm just going to say it like this. He

00:44:56.160 --> 00:45:00.670
carries himself very

00:45:00.670 --> 00:45:00.680
confidently,

00:45:00.680 --> 00:45:04.550
very poised in the way he

00:45:04.560 --> 00:45:07.829
talked, similar to the way Barack Obama

00:45:07.839 --> 00:45:09.990
used to whenever he delivered his

00:45:10.000 --> 00:45:11.910
speeches to the State of the

00:45:11.920 --> 00:45:13.990
Union. The way he carried

00:45:14.000 --> 00:45:17.630
himself, he spoke very

00:45:17.630 --> 00:45:17.640
intelligently;

00:45:17.640 --> 00:45:22.750
he

00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:25.589
was very

00:45:25.599 --> 00:45:28.190
poised

00:45:28.190 --> 00:45:28.200
and

00:45:28.200 --> 00:45:34.069
very precise. He had a way

00:45:34.079 --> 00:45:39.109
to draw you in; he made you like him. It

00:45:39.119 --> 00:45:43.190
was so peaceful, and the way he

00:45:43.200 --> 00:45:47.630
communicated to you

00:45:47.640 --> 00:45:50.630
just brought peace. It

00:45:50.640 --> 00:45:53.430
was really weird, very strange because

00:45:53.440 --> 00:45:56.150
everybody was just fixated on his

00:45:56.160 --> 00:45:58.390
face.

00:45:58.400 --> 00:45:59.790
He brought the

00:45:59.800 --> 00:46:02.630
peace they used to feel, the peace I told

00:46:02.640 --> 00:46:05.990
you about at the beginning that you

00:46:06.000 --> 00:46:08.150
didn't feel anymore. He brought that

00:46:08.160 --> 00:46:10.950
peace you didn't feel. He brought

00:46:10.960 --> 00:46:14.230
that sense of comfort that I said

00:46:14.240 --> 00:46:16.710
every person wakes up with every single

00:46:16.720 --> 00:46:19.750
day and goes to bed with as a

00:46:19.760 --> 00:46:21.829
sinner; they don't even realize it. And

00:46:21.839 --> 00:46:23.990
that's peace. It's like a prayer

00:46:24.000 --> 00:46:25.829
covering that the body of Christ brings

00:46:25.839 --> 00:46:28.950
into this world, and we

00:46:28.950 --> 00:46:28.960
probably

00:46:28.960 --> 00:46:30.870
don't even realize that

00:46:30.880 --> 00:46:32.630
we bring it. The church doesn't even

00:46:32.640 --> 00:46:34.790
realize the power they have,

00:46:34.800 --> 00:46:36.950
the atmosphere we create

00:46:36.960 --> 00:46:39.510
with our prayers, the atmosphere we

00:46:39.520 --> 00:46:41.150
create

00:46:41.160 --> 00:46:45.910
every day. And then when we're gone,

00:46:45.920 --> 00:46:49.750
it's hell on earth. It's awful. And for

00:46:49.760 --> 00:46:52.870
the first time, why he is so attractive

00:46:52.880 --> 00:46:55.030
is when he speaks, nobody else feels

00:46:55.040 --> 00:46:58.270
that anymore. But he has a falseness, a

00:46:58.280 --> 00:47:02.710
false peace that everybody pursues and

00:47:02.720 --> 00:47:05.589
wants. Again, they're starving for it;

00:47:05.599 --> 00:47:07.589
they don't have it, and so they're

00:47:07.599 --> 00:47:09.510
looking for it. And he has a dirtiness;

00:47:09.520 --> 00:47:11.670
it's a dirty

00:47:11.670 --> 00:47:11.680
falseness

00:47:11.680 --> 00:47:13.589
that they're all wanting,

00:47:13.599 --> 00:47:17.510
they're all looking for again. And so he

00:47:17.520 --> 00:47:18.510
sucks you

00:47:18.520 --> 00:47:22.109
in.

00:47:22.119 --> 00:47:24.670
At this

00:47:24.680 --> 00:47:27.829
time,

00:47:27.829 --> 00:47:27.839
during

00:47:27.839 --> 00:47:29.829
this part of the visitation,

00:47:29.839 --> 00:47:33.910
I'm taken out of the earth.

00:47:33.920 --> 00:47:36.470
I'm sucked up out of the earth and

00:47:36.480 --> 00:47:41.670
I go to the edge of heaven and earth,

00:47:41.680 --> 00:47:43.510
and I'm standing there. I can turn

00:47:43.520 --> 00:47:45.109
around and I can look and I see the

00:47:45.119 --> 00:47:47.790
gates of heaven. I see the holy city is

00:47:47.800 --> 00:47:51.430
beautiful all behind me, and Jesus is

00:47:51.440 --> 00:47:55.309
standing right here this time on my

00:47:55.319 --> 00:47:56.829
left.

00:47:56.839 --> 00:48:00.309
And he speaks to me this time and he

00:48:00.319 --> 00:48:02.870
says, 'Look at the earth; I want to show

00:48:02.880 --> 00:48:04.829
you something that's about to take

00:48:04.829 --> 00:48:04.839
place.'And

00:48:04.839 --> 00:48:07.589
I said,

00:48:07.599 --> 00:48:09.349
'You know, I'm just excited.'I look

00:48:09.359 --> 00:48:12.470
over and I look at the earth and

00:48:12.480 --> 00:48:14.790
it's spinning; I can see it

00:48:14.800 --> 00:48:17.270
moving. And he said, 'Do you

00:48:17.280 --> 00:48:19.829
see each one of those lights down

00:48:19.829 --> 00:48:19.839
there?'And

00:48:19.839 --> 00:48:21.349
I said, 'Yeah.'He goes, 'Those

00:48:21.359 --> 00:48:23.910
represent

00:48:23.910 --> 00:48:23.920
souls.'And

00:48:23.920 --> 00:48:26.630
he said there is going to

00:48:26.640 --> 00:48:30.630
be a major revival about to happen

00:48:30.640 --> 00:48:33.630
throughout the

00:48:33.630 --> 00:48:33.640
earth—a

00:48:33.640 --> 00:48:38.950
final push, a final harvest, a

00:48:38.950 --> 00:48:38.960
China

00:48:38.960 --> 00:48:41.309
major harvest. It's

00:48:41.309 --> 00:48:41.319
like—and

00:48:41.319 --> 00:48:44.390
I don't want to add any

00:48:44.400 --> 00:48:46.230
words that he didn't say, but that's

00:48:46.240 --> 00:48:48.950
what he showed me. And

00:48:48.960 --> 00:48:50.790
then he started—I look over at

00:48:50.800 --> 00:48:53.030
him, I'm looking over, and I look at his

00:48:53.040 --> 00:48:55.109
eyes and they're welled up with

00:48:55.119 --> 00:48:58.270
tears. He said, 'Do you see

00:48:58.270 --> 00:48:58.280
China?'And

00:48:58.280 --> 00:49:01.309
I said, 'Yeah.'He said,

00:49:01.319 --> 00:49:05.470
'They, a lot of them, died for my

00:49:05.470 --> 00:49:05.480
gospel.'"The

00:49:05.480 --> 00:49:09.950
gospel cost them something,

00:49:09.950 --> 00:49:09.960
Brandon."He

00:49:09.960 --> 00:49:12.790
looked at him and was so

00:49:12.800 --> 00:49:15.990
filled with joy at the sacrifice

00:49:16.000 --> 00:49:18.870
they gave for the gospel.

00:49:18.880 --> 00:49:21.349
What I saw

00:49:21.359 --> 00:49:23.990
when I was looking over were these gold

00:49:24.000 --> 00:49:27.190
streams. They were like gold

00:49:27.200 --> 00:49:29.589
streets, but they weren't, because I knew

00:49:29.599 --> 00:49:31.430
each one of those lights represented a

00:49:31.440 --> 00:49:33.910
soul. I said, "Lord, what is

00:49:33.910 --> 00:49:33.920
that?"He

00:49:33.920 --> 00:49:36.510
said, "That's the underground

00:49:36.520 --> 00:49:38.910
churches in

00:49:38.910 --> 00:49:38.920
China."He

00:49:38.920 --> 00:49:42.710
said, "Each one of those

00:49:42.710 --> 00:49:42.720
represents

00:49:42.720 --> 00:49:44.950
a

00:49:44.950 --> 00:49:44.960
soul."It's

00:49:44.960 --> 00:49:47.510
just amazing

00:49:47.520 --> 00:49:49.630
because I'm looking at the

00:49:49.630 --> 00:49:49.640
Asian

00:49:49.640 --> 00:49:52.390
souls that get saved and

00:49:52.400 --> 00:49:55.589
they spread all throughout Asia. You can

00:49:55.599 --> 00:50:00.069
see these gold veins that go up

00:50:00.079 --> 00:50:02.870
through North Korea, South

00:50:02.880 --> 00:50:07.750
Korea, and Japan.

00:50:07.760 --> 00:50:10.150
Then I

00:50:10.150 --> 00:50:10.160
looked

00:50:10.160 --> 00:50:11.910
over at the

00:50:11.920 --> 00:50:13.430
Philippines and there were lights in the

00:50:13.440 --> 00:50:15.990
Philippines. Then I looked at Australia

00:50:16.000 --> 00:50:18.390
and there were lights in Australia, and there

00:50:18.390 --> 00:50:18.400
were

00:50:18.400 --> 00:50:20.270
these circles, like crop

00:50:20.280 --> 00:50:24.230
circles,

00:50:27.520 --> 00:50:30.670
all over

00:50:30.680 --> 00:50:35.349
Europe, including France and Germany. Each country

00:50:35.359 --> 00:50:39.030
had a circle, and some circles were

00:50:39.040 --> 00:50:41.910
bigger than others. Inside each

00:50:41.910 --> 00:50:41.920
of

00:50:41.920 --> 00:50:44.870
those circles were lights.

00:50:44.880 --> 00:50:47.270
They

00:50:47.280 --> 00:50:49.510
represented

00:50:49.520 --> 00:50:51.710
hotspots for

00:50:51.720 --> 00:50:55.349
revival, major places where people went

00:50:55.359 --> 00:50:58.069
for revival.

00:50:58.079 --> 00:50:59.990
The Lord never said what they represent while I

00:51:00.000 --> 00:51:01.750
was standing there;

00:51:01.760 --> 00:51:03.750
he just told me to look at the souls.

00:51:03.760 --> 00:51:06.790
But

00:51:06.800 --> 00:51:08.790
they were all round circles.

00:51:08.800 --> 00:51:10.870
Then I looked over to the Middle East,

00:51:10.880 --> 00:51:13.510
and there weren't as many

00:51:13.510 --> 00:51:13.520
there

00:51:13.520 --> 00:51:17.349
as there were in Africa,

00:51:17.359 --> 00:51:19.030
Europe,

00:51:19.040 --> 00:51:21.510
America, Canada, Mexico, and

00:51:21.520 --> 00:51:24.390
South America. In Pakistan, Afghanistan,

00:51:24.390 --> 00:51:24.400
Iraq, and Iran,

00:51:24.400 --> 00:51:26.309
there was

00:51:28.800 --> 00:51:31.430
revival.

00:51:31.440 --> 00:51:34.470
People were getting

00:51:34.480 --> 00:51:38.230
saved and led to the Lord

00:51:38.240 --> 00:51:40.549
there; there was revival there. I'm not

00:51:40.559 --> 00:51:42.390
saying there wasn't; there

00:51:42.400 --> 00:51:44.790
still was, but it didn't

00:51:44.800 --> 00:51:48.069
seem as significant as

00:51:48.079 --> 00:51:50.150
some of the other places I saw,

00:51:50.150 --> 00:51:50.160
though

00:51:50.160 --> 00:51:52.710
it was amazing all over the

00:51:52.720 --> 00:51:58.109
place. America, from coast to

00:51:58.119 --> 00:52:02.430
coast, was lights

00:52:02.430 --> 00:52:02.440
everywhere—literally

00:52:02.440 --> 00:52:05.030
hundreds of

00:52:05.040 --> 00:52:09.390
thousands, if not millions, of lights

00:52:09.400 --> 00:52:12.390
everywhere. They went all up and

00:52:12.400 --> 00:52:16.910
down the I-35 corridor from Texas to

00:52:16.920 --> 00:52:20.470
Oklahoma. There were major places of

00:52:20.480 --> 00:52:24.950
revival there. Then I saw

00:52:28.520 --> 00:52:31.430
major revival on the West Coast

00:52:31.440 --> 00:52:32.710
and the East Coast. I mean, it was

00:52:32.720 --> 00:52:35.190
everywhere. The revival was everywhere.

00:52:35.200 --> 00:52:37.950
But I know that...

00:52:37.960 --> 00:52:41.270
let me see this. Then,

00:52:41.280 --> 00:52:43.589
what else did I see? I went up

00:52:43.599 --> 00:52:46.910
and I looked behind me,

00:52:46.920 --> 00:52:50.470
and there was a wave coming out of

00:52:50.480 --> 00:52:52.470
heaven on the edge of heaven.

00:52:52.480 --> 00:52:55.430
There was like a wall, and on this wall,

00:52:55.440 --> 00:52:58.870
this massive golden brick wall around

00:52:58.870 --> 00:52:58.880
heaven—a

00:52:58.880 --> 00:53:02.510
massive, thick wall.

00:53:02.520 --> 00:53:07.109
And there was a wave.

00:53:07.119 --> 00:53:12.390
This wave was huge, like a tsunami

00:53:12.390 --> 00:53:12.400
wave—the

00:53:12.400 --> 00:53:15.589
biggest wave you can

00:53:15.599 --> 00:53:17.670
comprehend. It was massive, like a

00:53:17.670 --> 00:53:17.680
50-foot

00:53:17.680 --> 00:53:20.309
huge, thick wall

00:53:20.309 --> 00:53:20.319
of

00:53:20.319 --> 00:53:24.069
water, and the Lord told

00:53:24.079 --> 00:53:28.470
me, 'This is the last

00:53:28.470 --> 00:53:28.480
outpouring.'There

00:53:28.480 --> 00:53:31.349
is an outpouring about to...

00:53:31.359 --> 00:53:34.670
this massive wave is coming upon the

00:53:34.680 --> 00:53:38.950
earth, and behind the wave were these

00:53:38.960 --> 00:53:42.270
angels, and they were all like

00:53:42.280 --> 00:53:45.349
soldiers on these chariots of fire.

00:53:45.359 --> 00:53:47.030
There were these chariots, and

00:53:47.030 --> 00:53:47.040
they

00:53:47.040 --> 00:53:48.950
were golden looking fire. It was

00:53:48.960 --> 00:53:51.829
the glory all over these chariots, and

00:53:51.839 --> 00:53:54.790
there were angels, and they all looked

00:53:54.800 --> 00:53:58.150
similar. They had armor on, and

00:53:58.160 --> 00:54:01.470
they all

00:54:01.470 --> 00:54:01.480
looked

00:54:01.480 --> 00:54:04.309
very

00:54:04.319 --> 00:54:06.790
similar to each other, and they had these

00:54:06.800 --> 00:54:09.670
gifts. They were boxes, and they were

00:54:09.680 --> 00:54:13.430
wrapped perfectly with bows on

00:54:13.440 --> 00:54:14.910
them,

00:54:14.910 --> 00:54:14.920
like

00:54:14.920 --> 00:54:20.549
presents, and each chariot had a box on

00:54:20.559 --> 00:54:22.870
there. And I asked the Lord, 'What are

00:54:22.880 --> 00:54:25.990
those boxes? What are those

00:54:25.990 --> 00:54:26.000
presents?'And

00:54:26.000 --> 00:54:28.549
he said, 'Those are

00:54:28.549 --> 00:54:28.559
end-time

00:54:28.559 --> 00:54:31.390
giftings, end-time

00:54:31.390 --> 00:54:31.400
mantles

00:54:31.400 --> 00:54:34.589
that have

00:54:34.599 --> 00:54:37.270
never been on the earth before, never

